        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                ἀγαθῇ τύχῃ <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Αὐτοκράτορι</supplied> Καίσαρ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Μ(άρκῳ) Ἀντωνίῳ</supplied> Γορδι<supplied reason="lost">ανῷ</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Εὐσεβεῖ Ε</supplied>ὐτυχεῖ <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">Σεβαστῷ ἀρχιε</supplied>ρεῖ με<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">γίστῳ δημαρ</supplied>χικῆς <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ἐξουσίας τὸ βʹ</supplied> ὑπά<lb break="no" n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">τῳ π(ατρὶ) π(ατρίδος) ἡ μητ</supplied>ρόπο<lb break="no" n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">λις καὶ δὶς νεω</supplied>κό<lb break="no" n="10"/>ρος Βέροια <lb n="11"/>θʹ </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> τῷ κυρίῳ ἡμῶν <lb n="2"/>Αὐτοκράτορι Καίσαρι <lb n="3"/>Γαλ(ερίῳ) Βαλ(ερίῳ) Μαξιμιανῷ Σεβ(αστῷ) <lb n="4"/>ἡ μητρόπολις Βέροια</ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ἀγα<supplied reason="lost">θ</supplied>ῇ τύ<supplied reason="lost">χῃ</supplied> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="2"/>εὐτυχῶς </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> τοὺς κυρί<supplied reason="lost">ους ἡμῶν ἐπιφα</supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/>νεστάτο<supplied reason="lost">υς Καί</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>σ<surplus>ι</surplus>αρα<supplied reason="lost">ς Κλαύδιον Κρί</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>σπον κα<supplied reason="lost">ὶ Λικινια</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>νὸν Λ<supplied reason="lost">ικίνιον καὶ</supplied> <lb n="6"/>Κλαύδ<supplied reason="lost">ιον Κωνσταντῖνον</supplied> </ab></div><div n="5" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Φλαυ(ίου) Κλαυδ(ίου) <lb n="2"/>Ἰουλιανοῦ <lb n="3"/>Αὐγούστου </ab></div><div n="6" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>DD</abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Valentiniano et <lb n="3"/>Valente <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von sechs verschiedener Inschriftentexte. Der erster stammt aus dem Jahr 239; der zweiter aus den Jahren 293-311; der dritter aus den Jahren 305-306; der vierter aus den Jahren 317-324; der fünfter aus den Jahren 361-363; der sechster aus den Jahren 364-367.</p>
            </div>
